# Icon Catalog System

## Icon Categories
- **art**: Painting, sculpture, drawing, photography, misc art
- **navigation**: New artworks, profile, sign up, explore, search, about, inbox
- **social**: Follow, message, favorite/like, pinned post, guestbook
- **commerce**: Purchase artwork, purchase made, accept/reject offer, shipping
- **action**: Edit, upload, pin
- **user**: Artist profiles
- **information**: City/location indicators

## Icon Data Structure
Each icon should include:
- `index`: Grid position (0-based)
- `name`: Human-readable name
- `id`: Unique identifier (kebab-case)
- `category`: Functional category
- `tags`: Array of descriptive tags
- `position`: x, y coordinates and row, column
- `cssClass`: CSS class name for styling
- `description`: Brief description

## Grid System
- 9 columns × 3 rows layout
- 32×32 pixel icons with 0px spacing
- Total sprite sheet: 288×96 pixels
- Position tracking for both pixel coordinates and grid positions

## Filtering and Search
- Category-based filtering with active state management
- Text search across name, ID, and tags
- Real-time filtering with debounced input
- Visual feedback for active filters